'From Squeak2.9alpha of 17 July 2000 [latest update: #2733] on 27 September 2000 at 4:50:13 pm'!"Change Set:		textFixDate:			27 September 2000Author:			Bob Arning- initialize a couple of BitBlt vars so that the string display primitive will not fail"!!BitBlt methodsFor: 'copying' stamp: 'RAA 9/27/2000 16:48'!displayString: aString from: startIndex to: stopIndex at: aPoint strikeFont: font kern: kernDelta	destY _ aPoint y.	destX _ aPoint x.	"the following are not really needed, but theBitBlt primitive will fail if not set"	sourceX ifNil: [sourceX _ 100].	width ifNil: [width _ 100].	^self primDisplayString: aString from: startIndex to: stopIndex			map: font characterToGlyphMap xTable: font xTable			kern: kernDelta.! !